Maven Module

---
<dependency>
    <groupId>com.anrisoftware.globalpom</groupId>
    <artifactId>globalpomutils-threads</artifactId>
    <version>2.3</version>
</dependency>
---

  * Api

  Public interface defines the listenable future and the threads;

  * listenablefuture

  Implements the listenable future;

  * Properties

  Threads pool that is contracted from the loaded properties;

  * Watchdog

  Watching the threading pool and informs the listenable future tasks;
